comments: Vucevic (ORL) establishes a legal screening position in Finney-Smith's (DAL) path and absorbs the contact.
Powell (MAL) places a hand/forearm to Vucevic's (ORL) back in the post but contact does not affect his SQBR.
Powell (DAL) engages with Gordon (ORL) in transition but contact does not affect his ability to defend the play.
Powell (DAL) establishes his screening position in Gordon's (ORL) path and absorbs the contact.
Vucevic (ORL) makes marginal contact to Doncic's (DAL) back and does not affect his driving shot attempt.
Finney-Smith (DAL) maintains legal position on Augustin (ORL) as he deflects the ball at the start of his drive.
Hardaway Jr. (DAL) makes clean contact to the ball on Gordon's (ORL) shot near the rim.
Fultz (DAL) makes contact with Finney-Smith's (DAL) arm in the lane and causes him to lose control of the ball.
Gordon (ORL) firms up on Powell's (DAL) shoulder during the screen but contact is marginal and is able to move through the play.
Gordon (ORL) places a arm to Doncic's (DAL) front during his drive but contact does not affect his SQBR.
Gordon (ORL) initiates contact with Finney-Smith (DAL) during his drive that affects his ability to defend.
Powell (DAL) establishes legal screening position in Gordon's (ORL) path during the pick and absorbs the contact.
Gordon (ORL) initiates contact to Powell's (DAL) front that dislodges him from his defensive position.
Augustin (ORL) commits a take foul on Curry (DAL).
Powell (DAL) legally contests the jump shot attempt by Vucevic (ORL).
Hardaway Jr. (DAL) and Carter-Williams (ORL) engage and disengage while rebounding.
